Spark connection, laughter, and intimacy with Loverzz, the all-in-one app for couples.

Whether you are in a long-distance relationship, newlyweds, or dating, Loverzz helps you grow closer through daily games, home screen widgets, and deep conversations.

Discover what your partner really thinks. One partner answers, the other guesses. Match answers to score points, unlock relationship insights, and ignite meaningful conversations.

DRAWING & WIDGETS
Send love notes directly to your partner's Home Screen. Use our drawing tools to sketch cute doodles or send photo widgets to keep your presence felt, no matter the distance. It is the perfect way to stay connected throughout the day without saying a word.

DAILY QUESTIONS & QUIZZES
From Future Dreams to Intimacy, explore over 13 categories designed to spark conversation. You answer honestly, your partner guesses your answer to see who knows who best. It turns serious relationship building into a fun, low-pressure game.

RELATIONSHIP INSIGHTS
Track your connection across 6 key dimensions: Vision, Intimacy, Adventure, Life Habits, Social Dynamics, and Crisis Management. Watch your understanding grow with visual progress tracking and compatibility scores.

PERFECT FOR LONG DISTANCE
Bridge the gap with digital interactions. The combination of real-time quizzes and Home Screen widgets makes Loverzz the ultimate tool for long-distance couples to stay synced and close, even when miles apart.

13 CONVERSATION CATEGORIES
Avoid running out of things to say. Our card packs range from fun to profound, including Future Dreams, Relationship Growth, Social Situations, Travel Adventures, Family, Career, and Intimacy.

WHY CHOOSE LOVERZZ
- Daily couples questions to build connection rituals
- Drawing and photo widgets for your Home Screen
- Deep conversation starters mixed with fun games
- Designed specifically for couples who want to grow closer

Join thousands of couples making Loverzz their daily habit. Because truly knowing your partner is the ultimate relationship goal.

Download Loverzz now and start your journey to a deeper connection.

MATCH, CHAT & DATE. IT STARTS WITH A SWIPE™.
With 97+ billion matches to date, Tinder® is the top free dating app and the best place to meet new people, with safety features that work to help you date more safely. Looking for love? An open relationship? Trying to find a date or new friends to chat with? Connect with local people everywhere on Tinder and get the best out of your dating experience:

Come As You Are: whether you're straight, gay, bisexual or anything in between, you can be who you are and find who you want on Tinder.
Date Beyond Photos: share your interests and learn more about your matches to get the conversation started.
Seek What You’re Looking For: set your relationship goals and make connections on your terms.

HOW TINDER WORKS
It’s easy and fun to find new people on Tinder®. Express yourself to make your personality shine in your profile and stand out to potential matches. Answer a prompt, share a little about you and show your face in your pics to increase your match-making potential. Use the Swipe Right™ feature to like and the Swipe Left™ feature to nope. If they like you back, It’s a Match! And with our double opt-in feature, it’s only a match if the interest is mutual.

PUT SAFETY FIRST
Try some of our safety features to help you make connections more confidently:

– Share My Date: share date plans with friends and fam, so they know who you’re planning to meet up with and where
– Get Photo Verified: verify your photos to help potential matches know it’s really you in that cute pic & increase your chances of matching
– Are You Sure / Does This Bother You: Tinder detects inappropriate language so people think twice before sending a disrespectful message
– Report a Profile: quickly report and block profiles with suspicious activity or inappropriate behaviour
– Block Contacts: take control and block anyone (like an ex) you don’t want to see on the app
– Video Chat: hitting it off in chat? Test your online dating chemistry and meet new people from home!

TRY TINDER PLUS
– Unlimited likes for you to catch feelings for as many new people as you want
– Use Passport Mode™ to match and chat with locals anywhere in the world before you arrive
– Unlimited Rewinds to undo your last like or nope
– Go Incognito and be seen only by the people you like

EXPERIENCE TINDER GOLD
– Get everything in Tinder Plus™, and try it out for a week before you commit to a monthly subscription
– See who likes you and match with them on the spot for faster connections
– Monthly Boost puts your profile to the top for 30 minutes to help increase your profile views
– Weekly Super Likes, because sometimes you really, really like someone

UPGRADE TO TINDER PLATINUM
Get most of Tinder’s premium features: join Tinder Platinum™ to get your likes prioritised with potential matches, send them a compliment before matching and more.

So what are you waiting for? Join millions of people worldwide! Tinder offers the most daters, increasing your chances of finding exactly what you're looking for. Download the best free dating app today!

Precious is the cutest way to track your baby milestones and see your baby's development. This app AUTOMATICALLY organizes your baby photos into adorable monthly pictures, growth slideshows, a photo calendar journal, and MUCH more — all with no work required from you.

Precious uses Artificial Intelligence to find the absolute best photos of your baby and uses them to create photo stories that will melt your heart.

You can watch your baby grow up with the then vs now feature, smile at a slideshow of last weekend’s activities, or effortlessly browse older baby pictures in the Photo Calendar. Every one of your baby's monthly milestones is accompanied by beautiful photo frames & collages, made for you. Have fun with your photos by exploring the hundreds of unique stickers we have available to mark the fun activities you and your baby share. 

You just keep taking baby photos. Let Precious handle the rest.

The Wyze app is your gateway to a smarter life and a safer home. Wyze, based out of Seattle, WA, makes smart tech at super-accessible prices, trusted and backed by a community of over 5 million users just like you.

 

------- This is where it all lives. -------
Shop, set up, view, and interact. Craft the ideal smart home for you and your family, and then control your smart devices from our ecosystem of affordable high-quality tech – all tied together in an app that won’t stress you out.

 

------- The cams that started it all. -------
Our first product was the trendsetting Wyze Cam: a multi-purpose indoor smart camera that helped our users keep an eye on what matters most without a hefty price tag. Now, Wyze has a full lineup of wired and wireless smart cameras fit for any occasion - whether that’s to serve as a baby monitor, capture proof of the pests in the garden, watch over your loved ones (including pets!), and nearly everything else. Wyze Cams are even more powerful when enhanced with our optional Cam Plus subscription.

• Wyze Cam Outdoor
• Wyze Video Doorbell
• Wyze Cam Pan
• Wyze Cam v3
• Wyze Cam v2
• Wyze Cam v1

 

------- Safety shouldn’t break the bank. -------
Keep an eye on your family and possessions with the award-winning Wyze Home Monitoring subscription, powered by our friends at Noonlight. It’s smart, straightforward, and ultra-affordable - that’s home security the Wyze way. For those that prefer to keep tabs on their home themselves, you can use motion and open detection from Wyze Sense alongside Wyze Cam detection notifications for self-monitoring instead.

• Wyze Home Monitoring Service
• Wyze Sense v2
• Wyze Sense
• Wyze Sense Bridge
• Wyze Motion Sensors
• Wyze Entry Sensors

 

------- Convenience from the comfort of your couch. -------
Switch up your ambiance with our line of top-rated dimmable smart bulbs including Wyze Bulb Color and its impressive 16-million color range. Don’t want to swap out your bulbs? You can add focused illumination where you need it with Wyze Floor Lamp for tasks and hobbies or convert your existing lamps, light fixtures, small appliances, and more into smart devices with our lineup of smart plugs.

• Wyze Bulb Color
• Wyze Bulb
• Wyze Plug Outdoor
• Wyze Plug
• Wyze Floor Lamp

 

------- Spend more time doing what you love. -------
Auto-unlock your front door when you get home, auto-water the garden, auto-adjust the temperature, auto-vacuum the floors, and more. Reserve your home time for relaxation and fun instead of routine chores using our lineup of friendly smart home devices.

• Wyze Lock
• Wyze Thermostat
• Wyze Sprinkler Controller
• Wyze Robot Vacuum

 

------- A window to a happier, healthier you. -------

Our Health and Lifestyle products are here to help you track your wellness, stay connected, and jam out to your favorite music. From smartwatches and smart scales to earbuds and headphones, we’re sure to have the perfect product for living your best life. Enhance your health tracking experience with our innovative Wyze Scale, now fully integrated with Apple Health. This feature allows you to effortlessly sync your health data - including weight, body fat percentage, water percentage, and more - directly with Apple Health！

• Wyze Watch 44mm
• Wyze Watch 47mm
• Wyze Scale

description:
HiWatchPro是一款基于蓝牙手环开发的app，使用蓝牙4.0通信，里面包统计睡眠、遥控拍照(通过手环拍照)，闹钟设置，久坐提醒（设置提醒时间防止用户坐太久），抬手亮屏、计步、消息推送、勿扰模式、睡眠监测、找手环等功能。用户可以利用app直观的了解身体状况以及运动状况，是一款轻量型助手型工具类app。


注意事项：
1，运动功能会使用GPS定位，在后台持续运行GPS功能可能会大幅消耗电池电量
2，HiWatchPro已接入HealthKit，可同步运行数据到健康
3，HiWatchPro所产生的一切数据，仅用于参考，不能当作健康状况依据。

Quickly and easily connect and control your smart home devices through SmartThings.
SmartThings is compatible with 100s of smart home brands. So you can control all of your smart home gadgets in one place, including your Samsung Smart TV and smart home appliances.
With SmartThings, you can connect, monitor and control multiple smart home devices quicker and easier. Connect your Samsung smart TVs, smart appliances, smart speakers and brands like Ring, Nest and Philips Hue - all from one app.
Then control your smart devices using voice assistants including Google Assistant

[Key Features]
- Control and check in on your home from wherever you are
- Connect your smart devices across many different brands to work together by setting ‘scenes’
- Build routines that are set on time, weather, and device status, so your home runs smoothly in the background
- Allow shared control by giving access to other users
- Receive status updates about your devices with automated notifications
- Talk to your devices using Google Assistant
- Track, monitor and save money on energy with SmartThings Energy. See how much your home and compatible Samsung devices cost to run, and try various energy saving features, such as AI saving mode, or schedule devices to run during off peak hours.
- Receive recipe recommendations by scanning meal kits, wine, and meat. Plan, shop and prep meals with the help of SmartThings Cooking 

※ Some features may not be available in all countries.

[App requirements]
Some mobile devices may not be supported.
- iOS 16.0 or later / iPhone 6s or later / iPad mini 4 or later

※ App permissions
The following permissions are required for the app service. For optional permissions, the default functionality of the service is turned on, but not allowed. 

[Required access permissions]
-
 
[Optional access permissions]
• Bluetooth: to find nearby devices using Bluetooth or BLE
• Microphone: Used to set up ultrasonic sensor-equipped devices
• Camera: Scan QR codes.
• Location: to automate actions using GPS (GPS optional)
                    Used to find Wi-Fi information to add devices with iOS 13 or later versions
• Contacts: Used to verify user information that will be used when sending text messages

Muslim: Quran, Athan & Qibla is your comprehensive Islamic companion, designed to support your daily spiritual journey. With essential features like accurate prayer time reminders, Azkar collection, and Qibla direction, it helps strengthen your faith and manage your daily worship seamlessly.

* Qibla Direction: Find the Qibla direction accurately, no matter where you are. The integrated Qibla compass ensures precise alignment for your prayers.
* Quran Access: Read and reflect on the Holy Quran directly within the app. The clear and user-friendly interface allows for easy navigation between chapters and verses, supporting your daily recitation goals.
* Prayer Reminders: Never miss a prayer with customizable reminders that fit your routine. Whether it's a gentle nudge for Fajr or a midday reminder for Dhuhr, you'll stay connected to your worship schedule.

Muslim: Quran, Athan & Qibla is designed to be your trusted spiritual companion, integrating faith seamlessly into your daily routine. Whether you're managing prayer times, reflecting on Quranic verses, or seeking solace in Azkar and Duas, this app supports your spiritual growth and devotion.

Download now and experience the convenience, guidance, and fulfillment of having a complete Islamic companion right at your fingertips. Stay connected to your faith, no matter where life takes you.

PURE is a dating app for curious people to show up in their most playful version of themselves. It’s a space to be honest with your intentions and clear in your boundaries.

Connect with like-minded community to create and explore new exciting experiences in a safe and supportive space.

Let your imagination go wild and get ready for amazing dates!

* HOW PURE WORKS?
Everything starts with Personal Ads. To see other people in the feed, you need to post your Ad. Write what kind of experience you are looking for and find someone who would share the same experience with you. Be creative and original with your ads, that's always appealing.

* IN PURE ALL BORDERS ARE OPEN
Paris, New-York or London? You can check any city worldwide and meet people from PURE community from around the globe.  

* WHAT HAPPENS IN PURE STAYS IN PURE
Photos self-destruct right after being seen, and in case someone takes a screenshot, you will get a notification about that. Also, all chat messages, including photos and audio, shared in chats cannot be saved to the phone's gallery.

* OUR MISSION IS TO KEEP PURE A PURE EXPERIENCE
Safety of our community is one of our key priorities. We are constantly improving our algorithms to find and get rid of scam and spam accounts, also our system sends automatic alerts on trigger words that might be used by scammers, so don't be surprised in case you will get a warning. 
Keep chatting anonymously via PURE and do not switch to other messengers. You know what they say: better safe than sorry. 

PURE uses auto-renewing subscriptions — you have to subscribe to get inside.
Here’s what you should know about PURE subscriptions:

- If you choose to purchase a weekly, monthly or annual subscription you will be able to go online and interact via chats with other users during the chosen subscription period. The prices may vary per country and are subject to change with a notice. Prices are clearly displayed in the app.
- All subscriptions renew automatically unless you cancel at least 24 hours before the end of the current subscription period without any limitations.
- Auto-renewal can be canceled at any time by going to your settings in the Apple Store after the purchase.
- All personal data is handled under PURE’s privacy policy https://pure.app/content/en/privacy
